In my dreams I am always saying goodbye and riding away,   

Whither and why I know not nor do I care.

And the parting is sweet and the parting over is sweeter,   

And sweetest of all is the night and the rushing air.

In my dreams they are always waving their hands and saying goodbye,

And they give me the stirrup cup and I smile as I drink,   

I am glad the journey is set, I am glad I am going,

I am glad, I am glad, that my friends don't know what I think.

- Stevie Smith

I don't think I've ever shared my Bar Method journey with you all! I have been a @barmethod babe for the last 4 or so years.❤️

What keeps my coming back are the results, of course, but I love participating in new moves! Bar has amazing modifications for pregnant participants as well as those with injuries or varying abilities!! It's addictive AF! 

If you're in the Portland /Lake Oswego area, try out your first class on me! Click my link in bio 👆👆 and use promo code: BARREWITHSHAHOLLY

The weekend is HERE, let's GOOOOOO!!!!

I'll be honest, I didn't think Bar was going to do anything for me when i started. "NO WAY is this exercise, I thought. " ... it only took one class to change my mind.. Bar helps lean out your legs, build your glutes, and strengthen your core. It's a low impact but truly a fun and addictive way to get and stay in shape. I can't wait to get back in there this weekend!!! Come join me! Just add a comment or DM me, and I'll hook you up with a FREE class. 🫶

 Hope to see you soon!!
